                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hart</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-02-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay directs Mr. Hart, if the facts are as represented in Department’s
                    telegram of January 22 last, to make firm demand, as instructed, without
                    specifying amount of indemnity, which depends upon further investigation.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
